Package org.openlca.core.matrix

Class ImpactIndex

java.lang.Object
org.openlca.core.matrix.ImpactIndex
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<ImpactDescriptor>, MatrixIndex<ImpactDescriptor>, Copyable<MatrixIndex<ImpactDescriptor>>
public class ImpactIndex extends Object implements MatrixIndex<ImpactDescriptor>
Maps a set of impact categories to a matrix index. Note that the index maps the IDs of the impacts so that each impact category needs a unique ID > 0 (which is the case when it is stored in a database).
